quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  71,11,"Yursili assamaa AAalaykummidrara"
  71,12,"Wayumdidkum bi-amwalin wabaneenawayajAAal lakum jannatin wayajAAal lakum anhara"
  71,13,"Ma lakum la tarjoona lillahiwaqara"
  71,14,"Waqad khalaqakum atwara"
  71,15,"Alam taraw kayfa khalaqa AllahusabAAa samawatin tibaqa"
  71,16,"WajaAAala alqamara feehinna nooran wajaAAalaashshamsa siraja"
  71,17,"Wallahu anbatakum mina al-ardinabata"
  71,18,"Thumma yuAAeedukum feehawayukhrijukum ikhraja"
  71,19,"Wallahu jaAAala lakumu al-ardabisata"
  71,20,"Litaslukoo minha subulan fijaja"
  71,21,"Qala noohun rabbi innahum AAasawneewattabaAAoo man lam yazidhu maluhu wawaladuhu illakhasara"
  71,22,"Wamakaroo makran kubbara"
  71,23,"Waqaloo la tatharunna alihatakumwala tatharunna waddan wala suwaAAanwala yaghootha wayaAAooqa wanasra"
  71,24,"Waqad adalloo katheeran walatazidi aththalimeena illa dalala"
  71,25,"Mimma khatee-atihimoghriqoo faodkhiloo naran falam yajidoo lahum min dooniAllahi ansara"
  71,26,"Waqala noohun rabbi latathar AAala al-ardi mina alkafireenadayyara"
  71,27,"Innaka in tatharhum yudillooAAibadaka wala yalidoo illa fajirankaffara"
  71,28,"Rabbi ighfir lee waliwalidayyawaliman dakhala baytiya mu/minan walilmu/mineena walmu/minatiwala tazidi aththalimeena illatabaran"
